description: Hello! Iâ€™m Caviar. The only thing Caviar knows for sure is that his mother was a sturgeon. The mystery of his father, however, remains unsolved. All he knows is that his father went out to buy groceries one day and never returned. Determined to find answers, Caviar has taken a fish DNA test. Could his long lost dad be a frog?
